## Stages (legend)

- **Brainstorm** — discussing concept, hypotheses, direction
- **Prototype** — building, no customers/revenue yet
- **MVP** — first users/customers, validating the model
- **Growth** — model validated, scaling
- **Execution** — stable phase, optimization

